{"tid":1677164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"眼紅者張宇人：「為左做生意，唔介意改變政治立場！」","createTime":"2019-10-27T02:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T03:35:40.000Z","uid":202464,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8bbdfe6da5ace4428f69286082c2e00a7f940a43","tid":1677164,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T02:32:26.000Z","msg":"張：藍店無黃光顧還被破壞<br />\n對於市民以政治立場選擇食肆，張宇人並無意見，認為消費者有選擇權，但不應破壞其他立場的商戶。他說有黃店吹噓生意大增，認為是個別情況。他說不介意有商戶為生存而改變政治立場，<br />\n<br />\n「今時今日的時勢，你扮黃有黃的人幫襯；藍的，無黃光顧之餘還要被破壞，自己要評估自己」。"},{"pid":"64caa111cdcd191306252c965c5fbf4397ea32e4","tid":1677164,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T02:34:48.000Z","msg":"讓大家重溫一下：<br />\n<br />\n當年佢提最低工資只可以20蚊的時候，<br />\n<br />\n舊登已經搵到佢係沙嗲王老闆"},{"pid":"d0666e0a69661cc84dbc2a6a435533e229c962cb","tid":1677164,"uid":31370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T02:42:22.000Z","msg":"廿蚊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468f97907fa0f01a7dc92d17a4188aa432a36cf4","tid":1677164,"uid":167658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T02:58:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">藍嘅，點解冇藍嘅人幫襯嘅？<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"f3a57043ddf11ecf7d2f33d09a00334c66ff170a","tid":1677164,"uid":202464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"468f97907fa0f01a7dc92d17a4188aa432a36cf4","tid":1677164,"uid":167658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T02:58:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">藍嘅，點解冇藍嘅人幫襯嘅？<br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:00:00.000Z","msg":"支那辦點解唔用維穩費支持藍店紅店？"},{"pid":"1b3dd4e59409168c2b777c491607c17e9a22b2d4","tid":1677164,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:01:48.000Z","msg":"點解藍店支持政府，但比當作 Condom ??? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{